<p><span class="anchor" id="p19"></span><span class="c2">(٥٤١ - ٦٠٦ هـ)</span> <span class="c2">(١١٤٦ - ١٢٠٩ م)</span> محمود بن عبيد الله <span class="c2">(٢)</span><a href="#p19" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p20"></span>بن صاعد الحارثي<a href="#p20" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
